title: Carrie Underwood Stops By For First Interview Since Return
itunes:title: Carrie Underwood Stops By For First Interview Since Return
description:
Carrie Underwood stops by for her first interview since her return. She talks about co-producing her upcoming album "Cry Pretty" and opens up about injuries she sustained from her fall.
